Dear Dirk and Romain,

	Here is my fix. The bug is in l.37 of <Rcpp/module/Module_generated_Constructor.h>:

instead of:

return new Class ;

it should be:

return new Class() ;


	Anyway, the patch attached removes this bug.

	Thank you very much.

Best regards,
Tama Ma


